headline: Portland General Electric (POR) Q3 Earnings Surpass Estimates
summary: Portland General Electric (POR) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +2.04% and -2.51%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
